/** * Return the logical AND of a list of {@code Nullability} * 
  *  UNKNOWN AND TRUE/FALSE/UNKNOWN = UNKNOWN  *  FALSE AND FALSE = FALSE  *  TRUE AND FALSE/TRUE = TRUE  *
*/

/** * Return the logical AND of a list of {@code Nullability} * 
  *  UNKNOWN AND TRUE/FALSE/UNKNOWN = UNKNOWN  *  FALSE AND FALSE = FALSE  *  TRUE AND FALSE/TRUE = TRUE  *
*/ public static Nullability and(Nullability... nullabilities) { Nullability value = null. for (Nullability n : nullabilities) { switch(n) { case UNKNOWN: return UNKNOWN. case TRUE: value = TRUE. break. case FALSE: if (value == null) { value = FALSE. } } } return value != null ? value : FALSE. }
